    "One solution could be the use of oracles (Berg et al., 2022; Dave et al., 2021), which is still an object of active development.",
    "Another topic of particular interest in current research is the design of front-running resistant AMMs (e.g., Bartoletti et al., 2022; Ciampi et al., 2022; Zhou et al., 2021a, b).",
